{
  "stem": "10698.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, please listen to me-- by then I had learned a little German.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I-- and I-- and I turned around and I showed him how my dress is in shreds, and I have to go in night-- night-- the shift to go to work at night.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and it's cold, and I'm freezing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he took me in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Meanwhile, everybody in the-- in the barracks thought that I am not coming back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He talk-- he took me in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My parents were praying there is some place in heaven for me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he took me in into the-- the-- there was a shoe store-- not store.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were working with shoes, and they were working with different things for--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were doing all kinds of tailoring things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He took me in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said you have something that was made something out of a heavy bathrobe-- the nice thick bathrobes that they used.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it wasn't ready, and he said, tomorrow you come in, and you get it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'll tell you something-- somebody up there loved me because I don't know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I came in, and they saw me alive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said wait until you see me tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because of that I have a kidney beaten down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because when they took us out from Skarzyska to Schonster Haus, and I worked night shift.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my three machines-- you know, they break down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So quickly, they had to-- they-- I didn't make the-- during the night, when the-- the-- the big shot from the-- you know, the commandant, came by, and I didn't have the amount.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they took several people out for the [NON-ENGLISH]-- to the place where they had the office, and they gave us a beating.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
